	abstract = {We show that the fitting of nonlinear hierarchical random effects models by max-
imum likelihood can be made automatic to the same extent that Bayesian model
fitting can be automated by the program {BUGS.} The word ‘automatic’ here means
that the technical details of computation are made transparent to the user. We
