\'{e}elles, illustrent l'usage de ces formules.},
	number = {2},
	journal = {International Statistical Review / Revue Internationale de Statistique},
	author = {Gauss M. Cordeiro and Gilberto A. Paula and Denise A. Botter},
	year = {1994},
	pages = {257--274}
}

